			"width": 216.03515625,
			"height": 145.8,
			"text": "Canvas API proxy\n+ rate limiter (leaky bucket,\nsemaphore 5–8, 403 backoff)\n\nLLM router\n(Opus ⇄ Haiku cost split)\n\nZero-retention on student text\nKMS-wrapped OAuth2 vault",
