			"width": 491.47998046875,
			"height": 145.6,
			"text": "Claude Opus 4.7   →  heavy authoring\n                              unit rebuild, curriculum mapping\n\nClaude Haiku 4.5  →  scale tasks\n                              feedback gen, summaries, classify\n\nGuardrails: BAA, zero-retention on student\ncontent, no training on student data, audit log",
