		{
			"type": "text",
			"id": "IZrESSat",
			"x": 120,
			"y": 990,
			"width": 608.4990234375,
			"height": 131.95,
			"text": "Prompt: \"Rebuild Unit 4 around the new NGSS standards, keep my rubric voice.\"\n\n→ Opus generates module tree, assignments, quizzes, pages, rubric-aligned.\n→ Writes ~100 calls in ~45s via backend batcher (semaphore 5, backoff on 403).\n→ Teacher previews diff before anything lands in live Canvas.\n\nCompetitors do worksheets. You do units. This is the demo screenshot.",
			"originalText": "Prompt: \"Rebuild Unit 4 around the new NGSS standards, keep my rubric voice.\"\n\n→ Opus generates module tree, assignments, quizzes, pages, rubric-aligned.\n→ Writes ~100 calls in ~45s via backend batcher (semaphore 5, backoff on 403).\n→ Teacher previews diff before anything lands in live Canvas.\n\nCompetitors do worksheets. You do units. This is the demo screenshot.",
			"fontSize": 13,
			"fontFamily": 3,
			"textAlign": "left",
			"verticalAlign": "top",
			"strokeColor": "#064e3b",
			"backgroundColor": "transparent",
