		{
			"type": "text",
			"id": "3SdEAjiI",
			"x": 1600,
			"y": 990,
			"width": 561.69140625,
			"height": 150.79999999999998,
			"text": "In SpeedGrader:  pick rubric criterion  →  bulk-feedback 20 submissions.\n\nEvery comment is grounded in a specific criterion + cited text span.\nNo generic \"great work!\" slop — teachers hate that, schools flag it.\n\n   Criterion: \"Supports claim with cited evidence\" (2/4)\n   Feedback: \"Paragraph 2 mentions the 1905 strike but omits source;\n                  add the Zinn citation you used in paragraph 4.\"",
			"originalText": "In SpeedGrader:  pick rubric criterion  →  bulk-feedback 20 submissions.\n\nEvery comment is grounded in a specific criterion + cited text span.\nNo generic \"great work!\" slop — teachers hate that, schools flag it.\n\n   Criterion: \"Supports claim with cited evidence\" (2/4)\n   Feedback: \"Paragraph 2 mentions the 1905 strike but omits source;\n                  add the Zinn citation you used in paragraph 4.\"",
			"fontSize": 13,
