			"id": "QmXMKzSs",
			"x": 160,
			"y": 1390,
			"width": 358.8583984375,
			"height": 207.34999999999997,
			"text": "Auth:        Personal Access Token\nOnboarding:  2 minutes,  zero IT approval\nCap:         ~20 AI actions / day\n\nIncludes:\n   ●  Chrome extension, all in-page tools\n   ●  Single-class workflows\n   ●  Fake-student sandbox (demo mode)\n\nWhy free?  Teacher-to-teacher virality.\nEvery free user is a district-sale data point.",
			"originalText": "Auth:        Personal Access Token\nOnboarding:  2 minutes,  zero IT approval\nCap:         ~20 AI actions / day\n\nIncludes:\n   ●  Chrome extension, all in-page tools\n   ●  Single-class workflows\n   ●  Fake-student sandbox (demo mode)\n\nWhy free?  Teacher-to-teacher virality.\nEvery free user is a district-sale data point.",
