		{
			"type": "text",
			"id": "pBL0uWCG",
			"x": 850,
			"y": 1370,
			"width": 343.255859375,
			"height": 263.9,
			"text": "Auth:        PAT or OAuth2 (teacher's own)\nBilling:     Individual teacher, credit card\nCap:         Unlimited AI actions\n\nIncludes:\n   ●  All free features, no caps\n   ●  Cross-course web dashboard\n   ●  Whole-course rebuild (Opus)\n   ●  Class risk radar\n   ●  Rubric-locked bulk feedback\n   ●  Export / scheduled workflows\n\nTarget:  power teachers, dept chairs,\ninstructional coaches.  Grassroots channel.",
			"originalText": "Auth:        PAT or OAuth2 (teacher's own)\nBilling:     Individual teacher, credit card\nCap:         Unlimited AI actions\n\nIncludes:\n   ●  All free features, no caps\n   ●  Cross-course web dashboard\n   ●  Whole-course rebuild (Opus)\n   ●  Class risk radar\n   ●  Rubric-locked bulk feedback\n   ●  Export / scheduled workflows\n\nTarget:  power teachers, dept chairs,\ninstructional coaches.  Grassroots channel.",
