		{
			"type": "text",
			"id": "LNszHi9I",
			"x": 1560,
			"y": 1350,
			"width": 374.4609375,
			"height": 282.74999999999994,
			"text": "Auth:        Institutional OAuth2 + SSO\nBilling:     PO / annual contract\nPricing:     per seat or per building\n\nIncludes:\n   ●  All Pro features for every teacher\n   ●  Admin dashboard, usage analytics\n   ●  SIS roster sync, standards library\n   ●  BAA + DPA, data residency toggle\n   ●  Audit log, FERPA/COPPA compliance\n   ●  Custom branding, training package\n\nSales trigger:  N teachers in a district already\non free/Pro   →  warm inbound to the curriculum\nor tech director.  Usage data closes the deal.",
			"originalText": "Auth:        Institutional OAuth2 + SSO\nBilling:     PO / annual contract\nPricing:     per seat or per building\n\nIncludes:\n   ●  All Pro features for every teacher\n   ●  Admin dashboard, usage analytics\n   ●  SIS roster sync, standards library\n   ●  BAA + DPA, data residency toggle\n   ●  Audit log, FERPA/COPPA compliance\n   ●  Custom branding, training package\n\nSales trigger:  N teachers in a district already\non free/Pro   →  warm inbound to the curriculum\nor tech director.  Usage data closes the deal.",
			"fontSize": 13,
